<Author>Limabre
<Content>do not go there unless you really need to The hotel is extremely basic, do not expect much. No room service, no minibar, and yuck, soap that other people have used, to save money.Also, people entered our room with the do not disturb sign on the door. Walls had spots and room smelled smokey. Do not go there unless you really need to. We had to pay to whole stay on the first night, otherwise we would have left early to another hotel. 
