<Author>yannes
<Content>An excellent hotel In some countries, this hotel wouldn't be a two-star (as it is), but a four-star hotel! It's very clean and tidy, my room was spacious and really tastefully decorated, the bathroom was spotless. I loved the breakfast room at the top floor, which offered a spectacular view of the sunrise over Berlin! The staff hardly speaks English, but anyway, they are all really nice. It's quite far from the center of the city, but there's an U-bahn station nearby, it's about 30mins ride to Alexanderplatz, and it costs about 2EUR. 
